t/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/squid-game-the-challenge"><em>鱿鱼游戏：挑战</em></a>参赛者065在被观众的烙印为“反派”和“卑鄙”之后，捍卫了他在大理石游戏中的动作。</p><ul><li data-cy="Paragraph" data-experiment="{&quot;widget&quot;:true}"><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/will-there-be-squid-game-the-challenge-season-two-3550855">会有“鱿鱼游戏：挑战”第二季？</a></strong></li></ul><p>新的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a> Gameshow基于<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/squid-game">热门的K-wrama，</a>看到现实生活中的参赛者参加了许多儿童游戏，以寻求456万美元的现金奖励。</p><p>但是，随着一些参赛者诚实地玩游戏，而其他参赛者则采用肮脏的战术（就像在K-wrama本身中一样），玩家被观众标记为英雄或恶棍。</p><p> Dylan（又名065岁的球员）由于在第六集中的可疑行动而属于后一类，他和球员399（Aurora）参加了基于大理石的游戏。</p><p>该游戏要求成对的玩家在20分钟内设计和玩大理石游戏，而失败者被消除了。但是，如果一对未能在时间限制结束时选出赢家，则两名球员将被淘汰。 </p><figure id="attachment_3546448" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3546448" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3546448" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1.jpg" alt="鱿鱼游戏：挑战" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/squid-game-the-challenge-netflix-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3546448" class="wp-caption-text">鱿鱼游戏的第1集：挑战。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>球员065和399是这种情况。迪伦因拒绝与奥罗拉（Aurora）妥协而受到观众的批评。迪伦还指责他的伴侣“提高自己的声音”，尽管事实并非如此。</p><p>最终，Aurora同意玩投掷游戏。但是，即使她是第一个在锅里拿出大理石的人，迪伦拒绝让她取得胜利，两名球员都被淘汰了。</p><p>受到迪伦（Dylan）的举动的愤怒，一位观众将他描述为<em>鱿鱼游戏的“真正的恶棍”：挑战</em>。另一个人说：“我不喜欢他在以一种正常的语气说话时提高自己的声音的评论。感觉就像是微观的侵略，”第三个回答：“哦，是的。我确实看到了。那是卑鄙的。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C0QYde8uVZj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342